      Ev satışlarında kapalı zarf ile ihale...

      Asymmetric Information
      when one party in a transaction posseses more information than the other.
      In certain transactions, sellers can take advantage of buyers due to asymmetric information, as the seller has more knowledge of the good being sold than the buyer.


